      "id": "PopularPost186476",
      "post_content": "This is an amazing card, especially for making an Ally deck.   \nIf one were to make one, this would probably be the Token card of said deck. As said above, it has a Commander-like feel to it, since it gives all Ally's counters.  \n  \nI just am wondering what would happen if someone tried to make an Ally/Spike deck (see [Spike Cannibal](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spike Cannibal))",
      "posted_by": "Ferlord",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost186476\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">This is an amazing card, especially for making an Ally deck. <br/>If one were to make one, this would probably be the Token card of said deck. As said above, it has a Commander-like feel to it, since it gives all Ally's counters.<br/><br/>I just am wondering what would happen if someone tried to make an Ally/Spike deck (see <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Spike Cannibal\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spike Cannibal\">Spike Cannibal</a>)</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '186476'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy54405\">Ferlord</span>\r\n                                (8/9/2011 7:54:54 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/Left